
"Your eyes are majestic!"
Majestic? What the hell does that mean? This is not how my life is supposed to go! This isn't in the script
"You should so sit with us all next week,"
"No thanks I-"
"Why are you not friends with us Olivia?"
"Well-"
"You're gorgeous. What do you think about my new haircut? I want your opinion on everything."
What the hell? Is what you may be asking. I know what's happening. They want me to say that they are pretty. They want to hear someone say it.
"I need to go home," I scoot past them trying to be subtle. "You should too."
Enough with the subtle! Run!
Author's Note:
Remind yourself that it's okay to not be perfect.